transforms.name: pinceau-transforms
transforms.result: :deep(.icon){width:var(--space-4);height:var(--space-4);}.has-dialog .left .navbar-logo{display:none;}@media (min-width: 1024px){.has-dialog .left .navbar-logo{display:block;}}.center .navbar-logo{display:block;}@media (min-width: 1024px){.center .navbar-logo{display:none;}}header{backdrop-filter:var(--elements-backdrop-filter);position:sticky;top:0;z-index:10;width:100%;border-bottom:1px solid var(--elements-border-primary-static);background-color:var(--elements-backdrop-background);height:var(--docus-header-height);}header .container{display:grid;height:100%;grid-template-columns:repeat(12, minmax(0, 1fr));gap:var(--space-2);}header .section{display:flex;align-items:center;flex:none;}header .section.left{grid-column:span 4 / span 4;}@media (min-width: 1024px){header .section.left{margin-left:0;}}header .section.center{grid-column:span 4 / span 4;justify-content:center;flex:1;z-index:1;}header .section.right{display:flex;grid-column:span 4 / span 4;justify-content:flex-end;align-items:center;flex:none;margin-right:calc(0px - var(--space-4));}header .section.right .social-icons{display:none;}@media (min-width: 768px){header .section.right .social-icons{display:flex;align-items:center;}}
